  heading: Architecture Design Lab
  details: 'An Architecture Design Lab is a creative space where students develop
    and visualize interior designs.

    It is equipped with drafting tools, models,
    and design software for planning and experimentation.

    The lab encourages
    innovative thinking, spatial understanding, and practical application of architectural
    concepts.'
